(do
  (def! l (. shape :left))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! h (. shape :height))
  (def! xc (/ (+ l r) 2))
  (def! yc (/ (+ t b) 2))
  (def! g (* h 0.2))
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (. canvas :ellipse (- xc g) (- yc g) (+ xc g) (+ yc g) seed)
  (. canvas :polyline
     [[(- xc (* g 0.3)) (- yc (* g 0.5))]
      [(+ xc (* g 0.4)) yc]
      [(- xc (* g 0.3)) (+ yc (* g 0.5))]
      [(- xc (* g 0.3)) (- yc (* g 0.5))]] seed))

scripts.script:
(do
  (def! g 8)
  (def! l (. shape :left))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! h (. shape :height))
  (def! xc (- r (/ h 2)))
  (def! yc (+ t (* h 0.65)))
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (. canvas :line (- r h) t (- r h) b seed)
  (. canvas :polyline [[(- xc g) (- yc g)] [xc yc] [(+ xc g) (- yc g)]] seed))

children.name: Slider
children.description: You can set slider position with "value" extended property (0~100).

scripts.script:
(do
  (def! l (. shape :left))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! h (. shape :height))
  (def! yc (/ (+ t b) 2))
  (def! value (/ (. shape :getPropertyValue "Value") 100))
  (def! range (- (- r l) h))
  (def! p (+ l (* range value)))
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. canvas :line l yc r yc seed)
  (. canvas :ellipse p t (+ p h) b seed))

scripts.script:
(do
  (def! checked (. shape :getPropertyValue "Checked"))
  (def! h (. shape :height))
  (def! l (if checked (- (. shape :right) h) (. shape :left)))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! m 2)
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (if checked (. canvas :setFillColor (. shape :strokeColor)))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (. canvas :setFillColor (. shape :fillColor))
  (. canvas :ellipse (+ l m) (+ t m) (+ l (- h m)) (- b m) seed))
